{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1000,"text":"I'm going to tell you about one of the world's largest problems"},{"time":5000,"text":"and how it can be solved."}]},{"cues":[{"time":9000,"text":"I'd like to start with a little experiment."},{"time":13000,"text":"Could you put your hand up if you wear glasses or contact lenses,"},{"time":19000,"text":"or you've had laser refractive surgery?"},{"time":22000,"text":"Now, unfortunately, there are too many of you for me to do the statistics properly."},{"time":29000,"text":"But it looks like -- I'm guessing -- that it'll be about 60 percent of the room"},{"time":34000,"text":"because that's roughly the fraction of developed world population"},{"time":40000,"text":"that have some sort of vision correction."}]},{"cues":[{"time":44000,"text":"The World Health Organization estimates --"},{"time":49000,"text":"well, they make various estimates of the number of people who need glasses --"},{"time":53000,"text":"the lowest estimate is 150 million people."},{"time":57000,"text":"They also have an estimate of around a billion."},{"time":61000,"text":"But in fact, I would argue that we've just done an experiment here and now,"},{"time":65000,"text":"which shows us that the global need for corrective eyewear"},{"time":69000,"text":"is around half of any population."},{"time":73000,"text":"And the problem of poor vision, is actually not just a health problem,"},{"time":80000,"text":"it's also an educational problem,"},{"time":83000,"text":"and it's an economic problem, and it's a quality of life problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":89000,"text":"Glasses are not very expensive. They're quite plentiful."},{"time":94000,"text":"The problem is, there aren't enough eye care professionals in the world"},{"time":101000,"text":"to use the model of the delivery of corrective eyewear"},{"time":105000,"text":"that we have in the developed world."},{"time":107000,"text":"There are just way too few eye care professionals."}]},{"cues":[{"time":110000,"text":"So this little slide here shows you an optometrist"},{"time":113000,"text":"and the little blue person represents about 10,000 people"},{"time":118000,"text":"and that's the ratio in the U.K."},{"time":120000,"text":"This is the ratio of optometrists to people in sub-Saharan Africa."},{"time":125000,"text":"In fact, there are some countries in sub-Saharan Africa"},{"time":127000,"text":"where there's one optometrist for eight million of the population."}]},{"cues":[{"time":133000,"text":"How do you do this? How do you solve this problem?"},{"time":137000,"text":"I came up with a solution to this problem,"},{"time":140000,"text":"and I came up with a solution based on adaptive optics for this."},{"time":143000,"text":"And the idea is you make eye glasses, and you adjust them yourself"},{"time":147000,"text":"and that solves the problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149000,"text":"What I want to do is to show you that one can make a pair of glasses."},{"time":157000,"text":"I shall just show you how you make a pair of glasses. I shall pop this in my pocket."},{"time":163000,"text":"I'm short sighted. I look at the signs at the end, I can hardly see them."},{"time":168000,"text":"So -- okay, I can now see that man running out there,"},{"time":173000,"text":"and I can see that guy running out there."},{"time":175000,"text":"I've now made prescription eyewear to my prescription."},{"time":180000,"text":"Next step in my process."},{"time":183000,"text":"So, I've now made eye glasses to my prescription."},{"time":188000,"text":"Okay, so I've made these glasses and ..."},{"time":194000,"text":"Okay, I've made the glasses to my prescription and ..."},{"time":201000,"text":"... I've just ..."},{"time":213000,"text":"And I've now made some glasses. That's it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":216000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":223000,"text":"Now, these aren't the only pair in the world."},{"time":227000,"text":"In fact, this technology's been evolving."},{"time":230000,"text":"I started working on it in 1985,"},{"time":233000,"text":"and it's been evolving very slowly."},{"time":236000,"text":"There are about 30,000 in use now."},{"time":238000,"text":"And they're in fifteen countries. They're spread around the world."}]},{"cues":[{"time":242000,"text":"And I have a vision, which I'll share with you."},{"time":245000,"text":"I have a global vision for vision."},{"time":248000,"text":"And that vision is to try to get a billion people"},{"time":253000,"text":"wearing the glasses they need by the year 2020."},{"time":258000,"text":"To do that -- this is an early example of the technology."},{"time":261000,"text":"The technology is being further developed --"},{"time":263000,"text":"the cost has to be brought down."},{"time":265000,"text":"This pair, in fact, these currently cost about 19 dollars."},{"time":270000,"text":"But the cost has to be brought right down."},{"time":272000,"text":"It has to be brought down because we're trying to serve populations"},{"time":275000,"text":"who live on a dollar a day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":277000,"text":"How do you solve this problem?"},{"time":279000,"text":"You start to get into detail."},{"time":281000,"text":"And on this slide, I'm basically explaining all the problems you have."},{"time":286000,"text":"How do you distribute? How do you work out how to fit the thing?"},{"time":290000,"text":"How do you have people realizing that they have a vision problem?"},{"time":294000,"text":"How do you deal with the industry?"},{"time":296000,"text":"And the answer to that is research."}]},{"cues":[{"time":300000,"text":"What we've done is to set up the Center for Vision in the Developing World"},{"time":304000,"text":"here in the university."},{"time":306000,"text":"If you want to know more, just come have a look at our website. Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":309000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}